<main class="content">
  <div class="section" style="text-align:center;">
    <img class="story-photo" src="images/couple-story.webp" alt="Justin and Jen">
    <h2 class="section-title">Does anybody read these?!</h2>
    <p>
      We met in the Boston area, while Jen was in residency and Justin was in law school. Justin lived right above Jen's favorite pho restaurant but we never crossed paths there (as far as we know). Instead, we met on the apps and immediately knew that we had something special. Within a couple months of dating, we travelled to Indonesia together and haven't stopped adventuring since then.
    </p>
